data.description: Welcome to Northside Commons!  This 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath home is tucked away on a corner culdesac lot.As you walk up you are greeted by the covered front porch that welcomes you into the open foyer. The first floor features the kitchen with stainless steel appliances, family room with a central fireplace, a flex room/office space and a formal dining room with tray ceilings. Head upstairs where you will find the Owner's suite with an ensuite which includes dual sinks, separate tub and shower and walk in closet. Three additional bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms round out the second floor.Step outside onto the back deck where you can enjoy the relaxing view of the backyard lined with a variety of mature fruit trees.Conveniently located near schools, shopping and dining! Schedule your Showing Today!
